result.description:
Søknadsliste:
Missing accessible name: The <svg> lacks a text alternative. Gjelder accordion(expnad-icon)

Søknaden om sykepenger:
Tilbake i arbeid: <svg> Missing accessible name (accordion)

List with one item: Found an <ol> ordered list or <ul> unordered list that contains only a single list item. Gjelder underteksten til søknaden, periode komponent, og error summery

Italic used: Text is formatted using CSS italics. Gjelder: kalender-komponenten for reise med 

Heading level skipped: One or more heading levels were skipped or used out of order. Gjelder landvelger tittelen.
Autocomplete missing: The form field is missing a valid autocomplete="..." attribute. Gjelder: filopplasteren
Insufficient normal text contrast: There is insufficient color contrast between the foreground and background of normal text content. Gjelder: kalender-komponenten for reise med bil.
Missing href: The <a> element is missing an href="..." attribute: Gjelder: Error summery

Søknadsliste:
Multiple header landmarks: The page contains two or more ARIA role="banner" landmarks or HTML <header> elements.

Missing bypass methods: The page appears to be missing common methods used to bypass blocks of content, such as a "skip to main content" link.

Multiple H1: The page has multiple <h1> headings.

Søknadsliste:
Duplicate headings: There are multiple headings with the same text or content.

Duplicate labels used: The form contains multiple <label> elements with the same text content. Gjelder: radio-gruppe
Title on non-interactive element: A non-interactive element has a title="..." attribute. (Gjelder steg i stegindikatoren som er inaktive)

Accordion expand, chevron, dato komponent:
aria-hidden used: An element is hidden from assistive technologies using aria-hidden="true".

Orphand label with no matching id: The <label for="..."> attribute points to a non-existent id.
Gjelder: All ekspanderbar hjelpetekst

No <legend>: The <fieldset> has no <legend> element. Gjelder periode komponenten

Non-active element in tab order: The element has been placed in the Tab order using tabindex="0", but it lacks a specific role="..." attribute. Gjelder: Error summery og filopplasteren

Input has no accessible name: The form control lacks an accessible name. Gjelder: landvelgeren
